<h1>习总书记明确反腐态势“新基调” 领导干部需找准行为准星</h1>
<div class="qq_bar clearfix" bosszone="titleDown">
<div class="a_Info">
<span class="a_source" bosszone="jgname"><a target="_blank" href="http://theory.people.com.cn/n1/2017/0108/c40555-29006302.html">人民网</a></span><span class="a_author">万鹏</span><span class="a_time">2017-01-09 14:36</span>
</div>
